translate portuguese adrian13_156a2700:

    # "My phone starts buzzing in my pocket. I pull it out and see that Adrian is calling."
    "O meu telemóvel começa a vibrar no bolso. Tiro-o e vejo que é a Adrian a ligar."

# game/Scenes/Adrian/adrian13.rpy:15
translate portuguese adrian13_bea5e8cb:

    # pc "Hello?"
    pc "Estás?"

# game/Scenes/Adrian/adrian13.rpy:16
translate portuguese adrian13_f9cf1bde:

    # gg "Hey, [pcname]. You busy?"
    gg "Olá, [pcname]. Estás ocupado?"

# game/Scenes/Adrian/adrian13.rpy:17
translate portuguese adrian13_e74e5c12:

    # pc "Not really. What's up?"
    pc "Nem por isso. O que se passa?"

# game/Scenes/Adrian/adrian13.rpy:19
translate portuguese adrian13_a2d441d4:

    # gg "There's this old arcade over on the east side of town that I haven't been to in years. I was wondering if you wanted to go check it out with me?"
    gg "Há um salão de jogos antigo na zona leste da cidade onde não vou há anos. Estava a pensar se querias ir dar uma vista de olhos comigo?"

# game/Scenes/Adrian/adrian13.rpy:20
translate portuguese adrian13_9ee91606:

    # pc "I didn't even know we had an arcade in town."
    pc "Eu nem sabia que tínhamos um salão de jogos na cidade."

# game/Scenes/Adrian/adrian13.rpy:22
translate portuguese adrian13_6580f309:

    # gg "Yeah, I think most people have forgotten about it. I don't know how they stay in business."
    gg "Sim, acho que a maioria das pessoas já se esqueceu dele. Não sei como é que eles se mantêm no negócio."

# game/Scenes/Adrian/adrian13.rpy:23
translate portuguese adrian13_7860a0fb:

    # gg "But I kind of wanted to go check it out, just to see what they're doing there, and maybe get some ideas for my arcade."
    gg "Mas eu queria dar uma vista de olhos, só para ver o que andam a fazer lá, e talvez tirar algumas ideias para o meu salão de jogos."

# game/Scenes/Adrian/adrian13.rpy:27
translate portuguese adrian13_34b5448b:

    # gg "Poggers! Come and get me?"
    gg "Poggers! Vens buscar-me?"

# game/Scenes/Adrian/adrian13.rpy:28
translate portuguese adrian13_4724ea78:

    # pc "Sure, I'll be there in a few minutes."
    pc "Claro, chego aí daqui a uns minutos."

# game/Scenes/Adrian/adrian13.rpy:29
translate portuguese adrian13_5b5160ba:

    # gg "Okay, see you then!"
    gg "Ok, até lá!"

# game/Scenes/Adrian/adrian13.rpy:33
translate portuguese adrian13_75da4880:

    # gg "Aw, alright."
    gg "Ah, tudo bem."

# game/Scenes/Adrian/adrian13.rpy:35
translate portuguese adrian13_c01438a1:

    # gg "Well, if you want to go sometime, just give me a call."
    gg "Bem, se quiseres ir um dia destes, é só ligares-me."

# game/Scenes/Adrian/adrian13.rpy:36
translate portuguese adrian13_ba01fe47:

    # pc "Okay, see you later, Adrian."
    pc "Ok, até logo, Adrian."

# game/Scenes/Adrian/adrian13.rpy:37
translate portuguese adrian13_225cc39e:

    # gg "See ya."
    gg "Até logo."

